body:
Has riot _actually_ done anything about the toxicity in low levels?

Admittedly I&#039;m on a smurf account, but it&#039;s disheartening to see obvious smurfs trash-talking new players or generally making the environment poor. 

I had a game a couple of days back with a relatively new player, they were asking for help and getting tips, but now they&#039;re so convinced the only way to win at league is to &quot;carry games, doesn&#039;t matter if your toxic&quot;

[Progress](http://i.imgur.com/ivZG6yH.jpg)

I&#039;m probably the only one who finds this a concern, but it does make me a little upset. :&lt;
